    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This light, brightly-colored scarf makes the wearer seem larger than life. He gains a +5 competence bonus on Intimidate and Perform (dance) checks.  If the wearer rightfully owns a kapenia and wears it at the same time as the scarf, he can glimpse memories of the history traced by the Varisian people in their kapenias and folktales. He gains a +5 competence bonus on Knowledge (history) checks and can attempt any Knowledge (history) check untrained.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item; creator must have 5 ranks in Intimidate, Knowledge (history), and Perform (dance); creator must be a Varisian</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Inner Sea Races",
